<h1>Introduction</h1>

<p>One of the most popular characters in Diablo 2, the Hammerdin is an iconic Paladin build that revolves around the @@@D2BlessedHammer@@@ skill. Owing to impressive area of effect Magic Damage that is very rarely Resistancesisted by monsters, the Hammerdin is the ultimate jack of all trades with unparalleled versatility throughout the entire game.</p>

<h1>Quick Reference</h1>

<h2>Skill Build</h2>

<p>The following section shows the core skills for the Hammerdin. For a detailed breakdown of all core and optional skills as well as the recommended order for allocating skill points, refer to the Skills section of this guide.</p>

<ol>
<li>1 point to all prerequisites</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2BlessedHammer@@@ - Max Immediately, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2Vigor@@@ - Max after @@@D2BlessedHammer@@@, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2BlessedAim@@@ - Max After @@@D2Vigor@@@, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2Concentration@@@ - 1 point immediately then max after @@@D2BlessedAim@@@, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2HolyShield@@@ - a couple of points immediately to increase duration, then max after @@@D2Concentration@@@, required</li>
</ol>

